cial Outlook for Medicaid|last=Office of the Actuary|date=2010-12-21|website=www.cms.gov|accessdate=2020-07-26|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828074903/https://www.cms.gov/Research-Statistics-Data-and-Systems/Research/ActuarialStudies/downloads/MedicaidReport2010.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在2009年到2010年，加州約有23％的人口加入加州醫療補助計劃至少1個月。<ref>[http://www.dhcs.ca.gov/dataandstats/statistics/Documents/2_1_Reporting_Year_FY2009-10.pdf Medi-Cal Program Enrollment Totals for Fiscal Year 2009–10] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120619021821/http://www.dhcs.ca.gov/dataandstats/statistics/Documents/2_1_Reporting_Year_FY2009-10.pdf |date=2012-06-19 }}, [[California_Department_of_Health_Care_Services|California Department of Health Care Services]] Research and Analytic Studies Section, June 2011</ref>截至2017年，Medicaid的年度總成本剛超過6,000億美元，其中聯邦政府提供3,750億美元，而各州提供2,300億美元。<ref name="Franco">{{Cite journal|last1=Franco Montoya|first1=Daniela|last2=Chehal|first2=Puneet Kaur|last3=Adams|first3=E. Kathleen|date=2020-04-02|title=Medicaid Managed Care's Effects on Costs, Access, and Quality: An Update|url=https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev-publhealth-040119-094345|journal=Annual Review of Public Health|language=en|volume=41|issue=1|pages=537–549|doi=10.1146/annurev-publhealth-040119-094345|pmid=32237985|issn=0163-7525|doi-access=free}}</ref>

